attributes.value: / # The Scrypto Standard Library
/ The Scrypto Standard Library is the foundation of Scrypto blueprints, a
/ set of minimal and shared abstractions on top of Radix Engine. It enables
/ asset-oriented programming for feature-rich DeFi dApps.
/ If you know the name of what you're looking for, the fastest way to find
/ it is to use the <a href="#" onclick="focusSearchBar();">search
/ bar at the top of the page.

defs.name: Decimal
defs.docs: `Decimal` represents a 128 bit representation of a fixed-scale decimal number.

attributes.value: / `Decimal` represents a 128 bit representation of a fixed-scale decimal number.
/ The finite set of values are of the form `m / 10^18`, where `m` is
/ an integer such that `-2^127 <= m < 2^127`.
/ Unless otherwise specified, all operations will panic if underflow/overflow.
